data.description: Welcome to 968 Calle Fresa. This stunning residence boasts 3 bedrooms, 1 bathroom, on a spacious 48,787 square foot lot (just over 1 acre). This Nipomo home is equipped with tile flooring, newer luxury vinyl flooring and paint, indoor laundry room, stainless steel appliances throughout the kitchen and a beautifully tiled backsplash. You can also enjoy cozy nights in the living room next to the updated wood burning fireplace. The property has potential to be an income producing property equipped with 4 full trailer hook ups, solar panels and 2 horse stalls. Make 968 Calle Fresa your new home! Contact your agent to schedule an appointment today!
